## Limitations

The findings are based on a limited number of sources, which may not cover all aspects of the complex relationship between perception and behavior. Additionally, some sources may not be peer-reviewed, potentially affecting the reliability of the information. Further research, including empirical studies, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the topic.

